					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I think he's Cain, actually. There's a few hints: all his stuff being made of leather, his forehead covered, his reaction to being told he's no murderer, but the most obvious being his name (ben Adam = son of Adam). And Bright's amulet seems to be one of the objects in Everman's trove:</p> <blockquote> <p>A picture of a girl waved at him from a picture frame <strong>sitting by a ruby medallion</strong>.</p> </blockquote> 
				 	]]>
